Package com.mimecast.robin.smtp

Class SmtpResponses

java.lang.Object
com.mimecast.robin.smtp.SmtpResponses
public final class SmtpResponses extends Object
SMTP response code constants.

This class contains all SMTP response codes and messages used throughout the application. Responses are organized by category: success codes (2xx), authentication codes (3xx), temporary failure codes (4xx), and permanent failure codes (5xx).
